This is the NEWS file for the x11vnc-auto package.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v2.0.0rc0 - 13 February 2025

Changes:
   XFCE4 Panel Plug-in. Added a plug-in for the XFCE-4 Desktop that allows
   active VNC viewer connections to be monitored and, if desired, kicked
   off of the system.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.0 - 2/5/2019

Changes:

   Changed the VNC timeout to 30 seconds.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.1 - 3/30/2018

Changes:

   Modified the socket service to bind only IPv4.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.0 - 1/11/2018

Changes:

   Modified the service to run x11vnc(1) under user 'rd' rather than 'root'.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
